&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Bank Community Nursing Assistant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hospice at Home&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Havens Hospices delivers a range of services to people with life limiting conditions requiring palliative care. We provide high-quality symptom management, psychological support, end-of-life and respite care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for staff to join our multidisciplinary Community Team. If you have an interest in palliative care, and the ability to enhance patient experience, we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Hospice Care we have one chance to get it right and help make every day count for our patients and their families. This requires Nursing Assistants with a commitment to patient experience, and the ability to work flexibly, enhancing the patient journey.&lt;/p&gt;
